description:
At Woodlake, the academic success of your student is our greatest purpose. We provide
a safe, rigorous and engaging learning environment, along with the life skills necessary to
prepare your student for college and a career.

Our goal is to develop confident, knowledgeable, active and civic-minded students. We
offer many programs to give students ample opportunities to explore, collaborate with
others and practice their skills. These opportunities are available during the regular school day and as a part of our after school program.
